summary: Buy now, pay later competitors don’t concern American Express because the credit card giant depends on wealthier customers.

headline: 1 Profitable Stock for Long-Term Investors and 2 We Find Risky
summary: Not all profitable companies are built to last - some rely on outdated models or unsustainable advantages. Just because a business is in the green today doesn’t mean it will thrive tomorrow.
